ActEconomic Action Plan 2014 Act, No. 1
Combating Counterfeit Products Act
Economic Action Plan 2015 Act, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing June 17 and 18, 2019 as the Days on which Certain Provisions of the three Acts Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing (1) June 17, 2019 as the day on which Division 25 of Part 6 of the ECONOMIC ACTION PLAN 2014 ACT, NO.1 chapter 20 of the Statutes of Canada 2014, other than sections 358.1, 358.2 and 367 comes into force and June 18, 2019 as the day on which section 358.2 of the Act comes into Force; (2), June 17, 2019 as the day on which subsection 7(3) and sections 23, 48 and 57 of the COMBATIING COUNTERFEIT PRODUCTS ACT chapter 32 of the Statutes of Canada, 2014 come into force and June 18, 2019 as the day on which a section 58 of that Act comes into force; (3) June 17, 2019 as the day on which section 67 and subsection 69(2) of the ECONOMIC ACTION PLAN 2015 ACT, NO. 1 chapter 36 of the Statutes of Canada, 2015 come into force.
